Spain Treasury to launch 18 - mth T - bills April 28 . The Spanish Treasury said on Thursday it would launch 18 - month Treasury bills on April 28 . " The Treasury is launching the regular issuance of 18 - month bills . The first auction will take place on April 28 , " the Treasury said in a statement . Earlier , Spanish Treasury General Director Jaime Caruana confirmed the operation to Reuters , adding that the new issue would be launched on April 30 . The Treasury confirmed the initial auction date would be April 28 . - - Madrid Newsroom + 34 1 585 2167 
